a.xlink:title: The PME GPU structure for all the data copied directly from the CPU PME structure. The copying is done when the CPU PME structure is already (re-)initialized (pme_gpu_reinit is called at the end of gmx_pme_init). All the variables here are named almost the same way as in gmx_pme_t. The types are different: pointers are replaced by vectors. TODO: use the shared data with the PME CPU. Included in the main PME GPU structure by value.
